        "2572": {
          "vnum": 2572,
          "name": "Tunnel",
          "description": "A winding passage twists through the underworld, roughly cut and filled with decaying debris. A slight breeze and the sound of water can be felt and heard to the southwest. Further passages lead northward and intersect with one another... the tunnel appears to be quite natural in origin. You have lost 120 experience.",
