        "2573": {
          "vnum": 2573,
          "name": "Tunnel",
          "description": "Sand and dirt mingle upon the floor of a natural tunnel beneath Mareldja. Passages twist and turn every which way, but the only ones big enough to traverse lead to the south and to the east. Launching yourself like a coiled spring, you BRUTALLY stab a slimy wet rat. (30) The ocean's energy begins to flow through you, granting you the speed of a gentle current.",
