          "name": "Sea`s Edge",
          "description": "You stand on a natural rock shelf at the edge of the sea. The swells are very small here, as this area is partially shielded from the sea by a westward shift in the coastline to the north. There is a small trail leading up to a road above, and an archway opens in the face of the rock to the east. The sea is to the west.",
