        "1005": {
          "vnum": 1005,
          "name": "Seawood Trail",
          "description": "This north and south running trail picks its way between a forest to your east and a cliff to the west. Fortunately the trail is wide and comfortable because the ocean, which you can see to the west, appears to be a long way down. Seawood Trail High-pitched chittering and distant screeches come to your ears from the forest to the east. Looking west, you notice that the land seems to drop off sharply in what is evidently a cliff. The cliff approaches the trail more closely to the south. The treeline you are following comes to an end as you look north.",
